DISCLAIMER — NOT LEGAL ADVICE. This dataset is verified by an automated,
primary-source-grounded pipeline (no attorney sign-off). Ballot-access rules change
and many figures recompute every election cycle. Records carry a `verifiedAsOf` date
and a verification `gate`; treat CONSERVATIVE-HOLD and BLOCKED records as provisional
and confirm with the Secretary of State / counsel before relying on them to file.
